{"type": "article", "id": 3903, "title": "可以涂鸦的围巾", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-27T07:57:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233112ngOE68zYUrTfICFK.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t你还在为今年冬天挑选一条什么材质的围巾而犹豫吗？香港 Little Factory 设计工作室最近推出了一款纸做的围巾 Paper Scarf。设计团队选用了独特的杜邦纸材料，这种材质的特别之处在于它的防水性、韧性与保暖性，柔软的质地也使得它与一般的纸区别开来。更重要的是，这款纸围巾可以满足你的涂鸦愿望，用户可以根据自己的喜好与创意，在围巾上写写画画，设计一条专属自己的围巾。Paper Scarf 的规格为 20cm*18cm，提供蓝、灰两种线条可选，定价 25 美元，<a href=\"http://littlefactory.com/collections/paper-scarf/products/paper-scarf-grey\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052331096Ceb0mMTkQAINnZj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233110s5CV2Q1moknbLrYc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233110vkL6B3VStMm9PuIi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233112vLZ387txDhqSeoau.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}